ormal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"232856da8b51f14f88e3be06959b59108ab65420","tid":1230471,"uid":50172,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T08:03:15.000Z","msg":"成架巴士都係黑衫，但除左冷氣聲之外乜都聽唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我從來都為身為香港人而自豪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f418b2d96e1415a8a360c280888d7f425dd5e896","tid":1230471,"uid":11254,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T08:03:45.000Z","msg":"今日出得黎都係有讀過下書"}]}